19:31.848 --> 19:34.255
There you are!
We missed you at the concert.

19:34.423 --> 19:35.519
You went?!

19:35.883 --> 19:37.717
Why did nobody wake me?

19:38.271 --> 19:41.736
Isn't there a saying about
not waking a sleeping fish?

19:41.883 --> 19:42.883
What?!

19:43.066 --> 19:45.252
It was the perfect family night.

19:45.377 --> 19:47.374
